<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p>As a rule of thumb, 30% deposit is required to start production, and the balance need to be settled before shipment. The catalog price shown is FOB Hong Kong. For order below US$3,000, an advanced full payment is required.</p>'=>'<p>一般而言，生產開始前需付 30% 訂金，餘款需在發貨前結清。 低於 3,000 美元的訂單，需提前作全額付款。 目錄價格： FOB 香港。</p>','<p>At EJI, quality is our top priority. Our factory QC team makes sure the pieces we produce are of high quality every step of the way. We have been a long-term member of the jewellery and manufacturing authorities in Hong Kong and have recently become a member of the Responsible Jewellery Council, we always thrives to reinvent our business to meet the new global industry standard.</p>'=>'<p>在 EJI，珠寶質素最為重要。 我們的質控團隊確保每一件產品在生產過程的每一個步驟，都符合高品質標準。 作為各香港珠寶製造機構的長期會員及RJC會員，EJI一直堅持生產高品質珠寶，確保產品質素達到全球行業標準。</p>','<p>For any other questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:enquiry@eji.com.hk">enquiry@eji.com.hk</a></p>'=>'<p>如有任何其他問題，請通過 <a href="mailto:enquiry@eji.com.hk">enquiry@eji.com.hk</a> 聯絡我們</p>','<p>Founded in Hong Kong in 1991, EJI is an established fine jewellery manufacturer with operations in HK and China offering manufacturing services such as ODM, OEM and OBM for wholesale clients and retail brands worldwide. With a comprehensive in-house teams, we are able to handle your order from design to logistic.</p>'=>'<p>EJI 成立於 1991 年，是高級珠寶製造業的領先企業，擁有香港與中國的業務。我們為全球的批發客戶和零售品牌提供 ODM、OEM 和 OBM 服務。 借助全方位的內部團隊，從設計到物流都能妥善處理您的訂單。</p>','<p>Generally, the lead time for ready to ship products is 7-10 working days upon payment or deposit depending on your order quantity and delivery destination. For customised designs, the standard lead time is one month upon receiving the deposit.</p>'=>'<p>現貨產品的交貨時間為一般為 7-10 個工作日，取決於訂單數量與交貨地點。 定製設計的標準交貨時間為收到訂金後一個月。</p>','<p>Samples are readily available to order for pieces from our existing private label &amp; wholesale catalogue, and are shipped via FedEx by default.</p>'=>'<p>您可隨時從我們的現有品牌和批發目錄下單，樣本將通過 FedEx 默認發貨。</p>','<p>We have a comprehensive operation that can accommodate a wide range of business needs, whether you are looking for ready to ship designs to expand your current collections, seeking a manufacturing partner to produce your own designs or a partner to handle both the design and manufacturing process for exclusive pieces, we can deliver with confidence that is backed by 30 years of experience. Please feel free to get in touch with one of our representatives for a consultation to discuss your projects.</p>'=>'<p>EJI擁有全面運營系統，能滿足各種商業需求。無論您想以現有款式擴展當前業務、尋找合作夥伴生產自己的設計，還是希望作產品定製，我們都能為您完成。 歡迎隨時聯繫我們的團隊。</p>','<p>We offer wholesale fine jewellery with no MOQ, you can easily place an order starting with 1 piece with our experienced and professional team via <a href="mailto:sales@eji.com.hk">sales@eji.com.hk</a></p>'=>'<p>從 1 件起。您可以透過 <a href="mailto:sales@eji.com.hk">sales@eji.com.hk</a> 跟我們的專業團隊輕鬆下單。</p>','<p>We specialise in fine gold jewellery made with natural diamonds and other precious stones such as sapphire, ruby and emerald. Other materials and metal are also available upon requests. Our diverse jewellery designs and collections are created to suit every occasion and milestone.</p>'=>'<p>我們專注於用天然鑽石及其他貴重寶石 （如藍寶石、紅寶石和祖母綠）製作高級珠寶， 根據需求提供其他材料和金屬。</p>','<p>Yes. We offer customisation for both our designs and your own pieces, with our catalogue pieces, you can customise them with your choice of gemstones, gold colour and carat, and brand the jewellery pieces with your own logo. For a more specific customisation, please feel free to contact us for further discussion <a href="https://waimingc1.sg-host.com/contact-us/">here</a>.</p>'=>'<p>是的。 我們提供設計定製和品牌服務。您可以根據選擇的寶石、金屬和寶石克拉來定製珠寶，並以自己的標誌為珠寶進行品牌塑造。 請隨時與我們聯繫，作<a href="https://waimingc1.sg-host.com/contact-us/">進一步討論。</a></p>','Do you offer customisation & branding? '=>'提供定製和品牌服務嗎？ ','FAQ'=>'常見問題','How’s the quality of your jewellery?'=>'珠寶質量如何？','What are your payment terms?'=>'付款條款是什麼？','What is your MOQ?'=>'我的最小訂購量（MOQ）是什麼？','What is your production lead time?'=>'生產交貨時間為多久？','What is your sample policy?'=>'EJI的樣本政策是什麼？','What kind of jewellery do you offer?'=>'EJI提供什麼類型的珠寶？','What services do you offer?'=>'EJI提供哪些服務？','Why work with us?'=>'為何選擇EJI？','editor-text-editor-e455955'=>'<p>如有任何其他問題，請通過 <a href="mailto:enquiry@eji.com.hk">enquiry@eji.com.hk</a> 聯絡我們</p>','title-heading-9f9fc43'=>'常見問題','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-1b28107'=>'<p>現貨產品的交貨時間為一般為 7-10 個工作日，取決於訂單數量與交貨地點。 定製設計的標準交貨時間為收到訂金後一個月。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-72c09f9'=>'<p>我們專注於用天然鑽石及其他貴重寶石 （如藍寶石、紅寶石和祖母綠）製作高級珠寶， 根據需求提供其他材料和金屬。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-89b95af'=>'<p>EJI 成立於 1991 年，是高級珠寶製造業的領先企業，擁有香港與中國的業務。我們為全球的批發客戶和零售品牌提供 ODM、OEM 和 OBM 服務。 借助全方位的內部團隊，從設計到物流都能妥善處理您的訂單。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-a72f0ba'=>'<p>從 1 件起。您可以透過 <a href="mailto:sales@eji.com.hk">sales@eji.com.hk</a> 跟我們的專業團隊輕鬆下單。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-a7b3b90'=>'<p>在 EJI，珠寶質素最為重要。 我們的質控團隊確保每一件產品在生產過程的每一個步驟，都符合高品質標準。 作為各香港珠寶製造機構的長期會員及RJC會員，EJI一直堅持生產高品質珠寶，確保產品質素達到全球行業標準。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-cb172ce'=>'<p>一般而言，生產開始前需付 30% 訂金，餘款需在發貨前結清。 低於 3,000 美元的訂單，需提前作全額付款。 目錄價格： FOB 香港。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-e3e4f0a'=>'<p>是的。 我們提供設計定製和品牌服務。您可以根據選擇的寶石、金屬和寶石克拉來定製珠寶，並以自己的標誌為珠寶進行品牌塑造。 請隨時與我們聯繫，作<a href="https://waimingc1.sg-host.com/contact-us/">進一步討論。</a></p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-ecb8fba'=>'<p>您可隨時從我們的現有品牌和批發目錄下單，樣本將通過 FedEx 默認發貨。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-ed78cb2'=>'<p>EJI擁有全面運營系統，能滿足各種商業需求。無論您想以現有款式擴展當前業務、尋找合作夥伴生產自己的設計，還是希望作產品定製，我們都能為您完成。 歡迎隨時聯繫我們的團隊。</p>','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-1b28107'=>'生產交貨時間為多久？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-72c09f9'=>'EJI提供什麼類型的珠寶？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-89b95af'=>'為何選擇EJI？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-a72f0ba'=>'我的最小訂購量（MOQ）是什麼？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-a7b3b90'=>'珠寶質量如何？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-cb172ce'=>'付款條款是什麼？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-e3e4f0a'=>'提供定製和品牌服務嗎？ ','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-ecb8fba'=>'EJI的樣本政策是什麼？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-ed78cb2'=>'EJI提供哪些服務？']];
